permissionTemplates.name: Default template
permissionTemplates.description: This permission template will be used as default when no other permission configuration is available

permissions.name: Browse
permissions.description: Access a project, browse its measures, and create/edit issues for it.

permissions.name: Administer
permissions.description: Access project settings and perform administration tasks. (Users will also need "Browse" permission)

permissions.name: Administer Issues
permissions.description: Perform advanced editing on issues: marking an issue False Positive / Won't Fix, and changing an Issue's severity. (Users will also need "Browse" permission)

permissions.name: See Source Code
permissions.description: View the project's source code. (Users will also need "Browse" permission)
